verbose_text: We reveal that Vegfr mediated expression of the atypical tetraspanin, transmembrane 4 L six family 18 (tm4sf18) generates a previously unknown positive-feedback loop that amplifies Vegfr activity to define the timing, magnitude, and robustness of EC identity decisions.
evidence: expression of the atypical tetraspanin, transmembrane 4 L six family 18
